                            <comment id="13802877" author="kaaveland" created="Wed, 23 Oct 2013 13:54:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I was the one asking about this on IRC earlier - just going to document that we found a workaround here. We made the bean implement Predicate and use when(bean) instead of when(method(bean)) and the error handling appears to work correctly.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
